author: kfogel
msg: Today I had a Biggie.  Usually I just have a small, and refill.  Why
pay more?  But today I needed a Biggie inside me.  Some days, I guess,
are like that.  Only a biggie will do.  You wake up and you know:
today I will get a Biggie and I will put it inside me and I will feel
better.  One time I saw a guy with three Biggies at once.  One wonders
not about him but about what it is that holds us back.
